is aligns with the system’s current intentional frame and bracketed assumptions. A mismatch triggers an explicit “hypothesis", "score": {"ratings": {"reasoning": null, "metacognition": null, "hypothesis_generation": null}, "novelty": "unclear", "is_unproductive": false, "composite_score": 0.0, "high_potential": false}, "model": "nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b", "timestamp": "2026-03-24T11:55:36.692693"}
