current IFS contraction ratios are too aggressive”) by treating those hypotheses as additional type formers, invoking the same abductive search to justify or reject them. This creates a tight loop between", "score": {"ratings": {"reasoning": null, "metacognition": null, "hypothesis_generation": null}, "novelty": "unclear", "is_unproductive": false, "composite_score": 0.0, "high_potential": false}, "model": "nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b", "timestamp": "2026-03-24T12:28:46.513938"}
